== Itihas ==

'bonderam', khore mhonllear bautte. Portugez kallar, don ganva - piedade ani sao mathiasa modem sodanch bhattank lagun zogddi zatalim. him zogddim soddovunk portugezan soglleam ximacher bautte laile.hem karia thoichea lokank avddunk na ani taka viroddh korpak tea bautteancher fator marpak laglea. heam ghoddnukechea ugddasak tornatte chole danddeank bonderam laun ganvant pursanv kaddta.<ref>[http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-08-20/goa/28309453_1_sao-mathias-sports-club-bonderam-malar Malar decks up for Bonderam this weekend, The Times of India]</ref>

==Somorombhnni==
divadde ganvant sov vadde assa. dor ek vaddo ap-aplo float veg-vegllea vixoiancher adarun toiar korta.festa disa ek pursanv kaddun tornatte chole and choleo hea floatsam mukhar nachta. bonderam disa ek carnavalacho vatavoron disun ieta.[[File:Bonderam, divar 2014.jpg|thumb|a float for bonderam, divar 2014]]


bonderachea fatravnnechi yad korpak, ho ganvcho lok fotashacho vapor korta. tefllam vo assalleancheo biyo kondyachea pokoll vatentlean zoran soddtat. heo zoran soddilleo biyo khub dukhtaleo ani haka lagun, sorkaran atamchea kallar hacher bandhi keli. 

adlea kallar Navelim, Goltim, Malar ani Naroa hea ganvchea communidade ho utsav monoitale. atam hea utsovak Goyche Poryatak khatem modot korta dekhun tache vyovsayikaronn zalam. 2000 voros savn Sao Matias(Malar) ganvchea lokan,anink ek bonderam utsovachi survat keli. ho utsov Divaddechea bonderam disachea ek sumana adinch monoita.<ref>Bravo da costa Rodrigues, Maria de lourdes. feasts, festivals and observances of goa, Merces: L and L publications, 2004.</ref>

